data.description: Great move-in ready condo in desirable location. Kitchen comes with Range, Refrigerator, new Microwave & Dishwasher. Washer/Dryer remain. HVAC is 2 years new and under warranty. Step outside on your private deck or relax in the living room in front of the fireplace, all depending on the weather.  The bedrooms have plenty of room, and the primary bedroom has private bath. Close to Malls, plenty of shopping and almost any kind of restaurant you might want!
